\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d055a1551d8b50a68f2b3b3558be86a3562624d","tid":355213,"uid":76815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:14:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>建議你驗血睇清楚 有個朋友同你一樣 最後先發現有淋巴癌e+仲醫緊 希望你無事</blockquote><br />\n情況一模一樣睇左幾個醫生先發現到</blockquote><br />\n頸冇痛wo 真係驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢都無 就係日日話累 同反覆發燒"},{"pid":"c47845b3e5e757456b708cae6850a85151f9cb86","tid":355213,"uid":55747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:23:41.000Z","msg":"你睇中醫已經可以俾到個病名你，太陽病"},{"pid":"263c367b36ee38b6f1c1fb5c1b17ae2d39186fe6","tid":355213,"uid":96979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:25:26.000Z","msg":"半身麻痺，腦係照到有野，但依加搵唔出原因，醫唔到，"},{"pid":"f528e13bd37790abaa997e58bffefa68dcfd25ff","tid":355213,"uid":69484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:26:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>半身麻痺，腦係照到有野，但依加搵唔出原因，醫唔到，</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591bf3f1c974a8c714a9ff4eaa7fe44f5f6c4941","tid":355213,"uid":69484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:26:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你睇中醫已經可以俾到個病名你，太陽病</blockquote><br />\n我會記住"},{"pid":"8cf3dca07cf5ad28f557e2ed5c46406a8cd41dcd","tid":355213,"uid":69484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:27:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>建議你驗血睇清楚 有個朋友同你一樣 最後先發現有淋巴癌e+仲醫緊 希望你無事</blockquote><br />\n情況一模一樣睇左幾個醫生先發現到</blockquote><br />\n頸冇痛wo 真係驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢都無 就係日日話累 同反覆發燒</blockquote><br />\n佢仲有咩病徵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class